B.ST=new A.L("1. Purpose","These Terms govern PerfectGest I (customers, budgets, cash, work orders, fiscal reminders, digital business card), with data primarily on your device.\n\nClient and financial data stay on the device and are not transmitted automatically. They may leave only through your actions (share PDF, exported backup, business card PNG/vCard/QR). See Privacy Policy.\n\nPublisher: Marcos Leandro dos Santos.")
B.Sq=new A.L("2. Eligibility","Users aged 18 or over.")
B.RE=new A.L("3. Initial Plan, trial period, and subscriptions","- Trial period: 7 days from the first time you open the app on the device (anonymous timestamp stored to prevent improper trial resets).\n- During the trial: up to 5 clients, 5 estimates, and 5 cash entries, including PDF. When saving the 4th record of each type, the app warns that only 1 remains. A 6th record (or exceeding limits) requires Pro Plan, even before the 7 days end.\n- After 7 days without Pro Plan: you cannot create new clients, estimates, or cash entries; you may view and edit data already stored on the device.\n- Pro Plan: unlimited use, encrypted backup restore, and interactive business card in the app \u2014 monthly or annual subscription via Google Play (price and terms in the store).\n- Auto-renewal until cancelled in the Play Store: Payments & subscriptions \u2192 Subscriptions.")
B.TE=new A.L("4. Cancellation","Google Play Store \u2192 Payments & subscriptions.")
B.Sz=new A.L("5. Statutory rights (Brazil)","Consumer Code may apply (7-day withdrawal where applicable). Refunds via Google.")
B.UA=new A.L("6. Fiscal reminders","Informational only; not tax advice.")
B.TS=new A.L("7. Limitation of liability","Management tool; user responsible for business decisions.")
B.Sa=new A.L("8. Intellectual property","Revocable license; no unlawful reverse engineering.")
B.SV=new A.L("9. Changes","Current version at URL below.")
B.Tx=new A.L("10. Governing law","Brazil; venue Caxias do Sul/RS.")
B.Ux=new A.L("11. Contact","suporte@perfectgestdev.com")
B.Yc=s([B.ST,B.Sq,B.RE,B.TE,B.Sz,B.UA,B.TS,B.Sa,B.SV,B.Tx,B.Ux],t.h)
