B.U6=new A.L("What is PerfectGest I?","A mobile business management app. Data is stored locally (SQLite). No PerfectGest cloud account for clients, estimates, or cash.")
B.TF=new A.L("Does it work offline?","Offline-first for daily use. Optional Google services may need a network when active.")
B.SX=new A.L("How does the trial period work?","7 days from first open. During that time: up to 5 clients, 5 estimates, and 5 cash entries (including PDF) with no paid subscription. When saving the 4th of each type, the app warns that 1 remains. A 6th record or the end of 7 days without Pro Plan blocks new records; you can still view and edit existing data on the device. Subscribe in Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription.")
B.U3=new A.L("How does the Initial Plan work?","The 5+5+5 limits apply during the 7-day trial (see above). After the trial or above limits, Pro Plan is required (monthly or annual on Google Play).")
B.Sc=new A.L("Where do I manage the subscription?","Settings \u2192 Google Play subscription. Cancel via Play Store \u2192 Payments & subscriptions.")
B.Tg=new A.L("What is the digital business card?","In Company, edit professional business details only (not clients or cash). Share card generates a PNG via the system share sheet. After your first card, without Pro Plan the card is static (you can still share the snapshot PNG); with Pro, edit and use advanced features in the app only (vCard, QR, interactive preview) \u2014 no PerfectGest-hosted web page.\n\nClients and financial data stay protected on the device and are not sent to servers automatically.")
B.Ue=new A.L("Are my client and financial data protected?","Yes. Stored locally. They leave the device only if you share a PDF, card PNG/vCard/QR, or an exported backup file (encrypted backup recommended on Pro).")
B.Ud=new A.L("What are fiscal reminders?","On-device alerts for MEI, Freelancer, ME obligations. Informational only.")
B.Th=new A.L("Weekly calendar, Latest entries, notifications, ads, Crashlytics, languages?","Weekly fiscal calendar in Company; home shortcuts to recent records; local notifications only; no ads; no Crashlytics; PT / EN / ES.")
B.Tb=new A.L("Privacy, deletion, suggestions?","Settings \u2192 Help and support for legal links. Wipe device: Settings \u2192 Data on this device \u2192 Delete all data. Feedback: Company tab \u2192 email suporte@perfectgestdev.com.")
B.a_k=s([B.U6,B.TF,B.SX,B.U3,B.Sc,B.Tg,B.Ue,B.Ud,B.Th,B.Tb],t.h)
B.vv=s(["\u0458\u0430\u043d\u0443\u0430\u0440\u0438","\u0444\u0435\u0432\u0440\u0443\u0430\u0440\u0438","\u043c\u0430\u0440\u0442","\u0430\u043f\u0440\u0438\u043b","\u043c\u0430\u0458","\u0458\u0443\u043d\u0438","\u0458\u0443\u043b\u0438","\u0430\u0432\u0433\u0443\u0441\u0442","\u0441\u0435\u043f\u0442\u0435\u043c\u0432\u0440\u0438","\u043e\u043a\u0442\u043e\u043c\u0432\u0440\u0438","\u043d\u043e\u0435\u043c\u0432\u0440\u0438","\u0434\u0435\u043a\u0435\u043c\u0432\u0440\u0438"],t.s)
