B.SQ=new A.L("1. Scope","PerfectGest-Clinica III is a clinical management system for Windows. The app stores clinical data locally on the device (MSIX container). The clinic or health professional using the software is responsible for entering and managing data.")
B.TQ=new A.L("2. Data processed","The app processes data entered by the user (e.g. patients, medical records, schedule, team). By default, we do not send clinical content to the cloud.\n\n2.1 Local data (by default)\n\u2022 Patients and medical records (health) \u2014 local SQLite\n\u2022 Schedule and operation logs \u2014 local SQLite\n\u2022 Local session/account and roles (ADMIN/DOCTOR/OPERATOR) \u2014 local SQLite\n\n2.2 Data that may leave the device (optional / by configuration)\n\u2022 Subscription payments: Microsoft Store (Microsoft Corporation). Perfect Gest Dev does not store card data.\n\u2022 WhatsApp Cloud API: if configured by the clinic, messages are sent to Meta (WhatsApp).\n\u2022 Firebase (optional): remote licenses and technical settings (no medical records).\n\u2022 Technical crash report (with consent): anonymous report with no patient data.")
B.RX=new A.L("3. Purposes","\u2022 Operate app features (clinical and organizational management)\n\u2022 Technical support when requested\n\u2022 Compliance with legal/regulatory obligations")
B.Tk=new A.L("4. Legal basis (LGPD)","Health data processing occurs in the clinic's context (controller). The software provides security and audit mechanisms to support compliance.")
B.Sh=new A.L("5. Security","\u2022 Access audit: metadata (no clinical content in logs), configurable retention\n\u2022 Encrypted backup (ZIP): AES-256 + HMAC manifest\n\u2022 Database encryption (optional): SQLite + passphrase in Windows Credential Locker")
B.TJ=new A.L("6. Retention and deletion","\u2022 Data remains on the device while the app is installed\n\u2022 Uninstalling removes data from the MSIX container; exported backups remain the clinic's responsibility")
B.SG=new A.L("7. Data subject rights","\u2022 Access/correction via patient record\n\u2022 LGPD report (ADMIN) in PDF/CSV\n\u2022 Portability via encrypted backup\n\u2022 Additional requests: contact the clinic (controller) or suporte@perfectgestdev.com (technical support)")
B.RZ=new A.L("8. Contact","suporte@perfectgestdev.com")
B.a1l=s([B.SQ,B.TQ,B.RX,B.Tk,B.Sh,B.TJ,B.SG,B.RZ],t.h)
